  <script>
    $(function () {
        //????????
        $(window).on('scroll', function () {
            var scrollTop = document.body.scrollTop || document.documentElement.scrollTop
           // var scrollTop = $(this).scrollTop();
            if (scrollTop >= 200) {
                $('#backTop').show();
            } else {
                $('#backTop').hide();
            }
            return false;
        });
        //????
        $('#backTop').on('click', function () {
            var speed = 0.08;
            var element = document.body.scrollTop ? document.body : document.documentElement;
            var top = element.scrollTop;
            if (element.scrollTop != 0) {//???????????????????????
                var timer = setInterval(function () {
                    top -= Math.abs(top * speed)
                    if (top <= 1) {
                        top = 0
                        clearInterval(timer)
                    }
                    element.scrollTop = top
                }, 20)
            }
            return false;
        });
    });
</script>

        //??????????????????????? ??1.?????#??????????????2.????___x
        //obj?????express??????callback????????????????????????????????filters?????????????bool?????
        function eachMemberByExp(obj, express, callback, filters) {
            try {
                if (express == null) return obj;
                var ary = express.split(".");
                var res = null;//??????????
                var catchRes = !callback;//???????
                if (catchRes) res = [];
                //???
                function eachMemberByExpSub(obj, ary) {
                    if (typeof obj != "object" || ary.length == 0) return;
                    var ass = new assert(ary[0]);
                    ass.value = obj[ass.key];//???????????
                    if (ass.value == null) return;
                    //?????????????a.name -> a.name[]??name????????
                    if (ass.type == 0 && Array.isArray(ass.value)) { ass.array = []; ass.type = 1; }
                    if (ass.type == 0) {
                        //?????????
                        if (ary.length == 1) {
                            if (catchRes) res.push(ass.value);
                            else callback(ass.value);
                        }
                        else {
                            //????????????
                            newAry = ary.slice();
                            newAry.shift();
                            eachMemberByExpSub(ass.value, newAry);
                        }
                    }
                    else {
                        if (!Array.isArray(ass.value)) { console.log("??[" + ass.key + "]????"); return; }
                        for (var i = 0; i < ass.value.length; i++) {
                            if (ass.type == 1) {
                                if (ass.array.length != 0 && ass.array.indexOf(i) == -1) continue;
                            }
                            else if (ass.type == 2 && Array.isArray(filters)) {
                                if (ass.filtersIdx < 0 || ass.filtersIdx >= filters.length) { console.log("????filters??????"); return; }
                                if (!filters[ass.filtersIdx](ass.value[i])) continue;
                            }
                            else if (ass.type == 3) {
                                if (!ass.filterFun(ass.value[i])) continue;
                            }
                            //?????????
                            if (ary.length == 1) {
                                if (catchRes) res.push(ass.value[i]);
                                else callback(ass.value[i]);
                            }
                            else {
                                //????????????
                                newAry = ary.slice();
                                newAry.shift();
                                eachMemberByExpSub(ass.value[i], newAry);
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
                eachMemberByExpSub(obj, ary);
                if (catchRes) return res;
            } catch (error) { }
        }

        //?????   type=0 ->  a.name     type=1 ->  a.name[]  a.name[0,1,3]    type=2 -> a.name[#id=1]  type=3 -> a.name[{0}]
        function assert(exp) {
            //?????___x?????#
            if (exp.indexOf("[") == -1) {
                this.type = 0;
                this.key = exp;
            }
            else {
                this.key = exp.substr(0, exp.indexOf("["));
                var m = exp.match(/\[[\d\,]*\]/ig);//??????name[] ? name[0]? name[1,3,5]
                if (m != null) {
                    this.type = 1;
                    this.array = eval(m[0]);
                }
                    //???????name[{0}]
                else if ((m = exp.match(/\[\{\d+\}\]/ig)) != null) {
                    this.type = 2;
                    this.filtersIdx = parseInt(m[0].match(/\d+/ig)[0]);
                }
                    //???????Diys[#Boxid="text"]
                else if ((m = exp.match(/\[.*\#.*\]/ig)) != null) {
                    this.type = 3;
                    m = m[0];
                    //??a=b? a==b     ?a!=b ????
                    m = m.replace("!=", "<>").replace("==", "=").replace("=", "==").replace("<>", "!=");
                    //??[]???#????
                    m = m.replace("[", "").replace("]", "").replace("#", "___x.");
                    this.express = m;
                    this.filterFun = function (___x) { return eval(m); };
                }
            }
        }
